 find that users, to a large extent, agree with community-created\nfact-checks. Altogether, our findings offer insights into how misleading vs.\nnot misleading posts spread and highlight the crucial role of sample selection\nwhen studying misinformation on social media.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 May 2022 23:27:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 01:07:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 1 Jan 2023 23:24:14 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2023 19:03:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
