m. Lastly, the result of the algorithm and the controller\nconstruction are demonstrated by application to an example of robot navigation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 13:12:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-30"}
