hat predictions for the radius valley for core-powered mass-loss and\nphotoevaporation become increasingly distinct for lower mass stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 14:46:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 20:08:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
