ers of\nmagnitude. Utilising additional GPU acceleration, we find that this speed-up\ncan be increased further with the generation of batches of waveforms\nsimultaneously. Even without additional GPU acceleration, this dramatic\ndecrease in waveform generation cost can reduce the inference timescale from\nweeks to hours.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 15:51:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2022 17:16:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 24 Nov 2022 14:16:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
